reviews.text:
This is gonna be one of the restaurants that we would not visit again. I really dislike their plates and some of the hot food in the salad area was rather warm.  The selection of drinks is more than food - the beers are actually not bad ($68/bottle).  No snacks nor appetizers as they think they have it all in their salad bar.
The seatings, environment, and the  atmosphere were pretty good tho.
western restaurant with nice salad, food is ok, no need to wait for seat, if they reduce the lunch set price a bit, will attract more people

Its another one of those all you can eat with a hundred bucks or so.  Quality wise is better than others. Soup comes in two different flavors and all is good. Salad bar on the other hand is with not much choice……choice fry chicken nuggets not too crispy though. Nonetheless its good value for money

Recommended the appetizer and soup buffet for lunch. There is bread at the soup corner. For appetizer it offers great variety of vegetable, but at the end of the table you'd find french fries with blue cheese and fried chicken lol. The place is kids friendly. Make reservation as it could get very busy.
Good burger the salad bar was empty and didn't get restocked while I was there but good for a quick lunch

reviews.text:
This is gonna be one of the restaurants that we would not visit again. I really dislike their plates and some of the hot food in the salad area was rather warm.  The selection of drinks is more than food - the beers are actually not bad ($68/bottle).  No snacks nor appetizers as they think they have it all in their salad bar.
The seatings, environment, and the  atmosphere were pretty good tho.

午餐buffet通常都不用排隊，而且有自助沙律吧很適合不想等候的我們。
今次第一次試吃厚切煙肉， 很特別很好吃，有點像中式的叉燒。
all day breakfast也很豐富， 看起來好像每枱都有叫這個餐，因為它放在店舖門口的照片很吸引， 事實上也真的很好吃，又有腸仔，又有waffle，而那個鹹魚沙律真的很特別，記得之前在某個地方吃過，可是已經忘記了是哪裏，現在可以回味這個沙律的味道真的不錯。
而自助沙律吧，最喜愛吃菠蘿和蝦多士，蝦多士真的炸得很香脆，每次都要吃三四片才能滿足，正！
但每次都覺得有點可惜的是，他們的薯條，因為不夠香脆 和不夠新鮮，沒有試過他們的薯條不是淋的，差！
western restaurant with nice salad, food is ok, no need to wait for seat, if they reduce the lunch set price a bit, will attract more people

今次係第二次光顧，適逢假日，我們預先book枱，去到嘅時候客人唔多，冇人排隊，餐廳職員建議可以選擇坐窗邊高台，我們四人想坐得舒服一些方便傾計就選擇坐卡位，Order主菜送沙律吧，不包餐飲，如果只吃沙律吧就$178，沙律吧很豐富，有雜菜湯和蘑菇湯，沙律菜、羽衣甘藍、辣椰菜、炸雞、薯角、薯條、沙樂美腸、芝士、烤南瓜、粟米、沙律醬青瓜鷹嘴豆、還有多款沙律醬，食材也很新鮮，主菜選了蕃茄焗豬扒飯，軟殼蟹意大利燉飯，龍蝦汁海鮮焗飯，雙層芝士安格斯牛肉漢堡，焗飯味道ok，漢堡沒有味也不juicy，餐廳環境舒適，gathering吹水好地方

Its another one of those all you can eat with a hundred bucks or so.  Quality wise is better than others. Soup comes in two different flavors and all is good. Salad bar on the other hand is with not much choice……choice fry chicken nuggets not too crispy though. Nonetheless its good value for money
